TextBody:
Hey Zeke,

Thank you for contacting Netwrix technical support. Can you please share a screenshot of the messages table for the AD Scan job?
 

Based on what you sent over, I'm just seeing warnings related to various custom AD attributes that NEA looks for out-of-the-box, but if these aren't attributes you use, they shouldn't stop the scan from running. More information can be found here: https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/z-kb-articles-salesforce/page/kA0Qk0000000divKAA.html

With the screenshot, I'll be able to get a better look though.

Thank you,

Tay Caliguiri

Senior Technical Support Engineer
__________________ _________
Cybersecurity That Works for You

300 Spectrum Ctr Dr #200, Irvine, CA 92618
www.netwrix.com
